Are you using the TrackballControls? TrackballControls seem to capture some of the mouse events in a way that other UI elements (e.g. a dropwdown box) do not work anymore.

In my case it helped to play around with the domElement parameter in the TrackballControls constructor, which controls where the mouse event listeners are attached to.

