It wasn't removed, just API changed:

``` javascript
// equivalent to THREE.Matrix4.makeInvert(scene.matrixWorld,inverse);
inverse.getInverse( scene.matrixWorld );
```

This is not anymore global GL state property. Instead depth write is now per-material property (similar to depth test):

``` javascript
material.depthWrite = false;
material.depthTest = false;
```

